title: How much should we budget for marketing?
body:
Hey Head Dao family! We would like to build more hype around the HeadDAO project and reward our holders more. But, from a marketing standpoint there is only so much we can do from tweeting alone. In order to achieve this, we feel it's necessary to be afforded a budget. We are humbly asking for 3-4 eth a month (on a LOW AVERAGE we bring in 33 eth a month for the Dao wallet). With this budget, we will be able to purchase several popular NFTs for giveaways on our Twitter for Head Dao holders . We have big plans in place for contests as well to reward Head Dao holders! With this we would be able to increase community engagement and bring in new HeadDAO owners. The marketing and social media team will not take any cut of this for payment, all the eth spent would go directly towards benefiting the project holders and hopefully raising the floor price. 
- The Social Media and Marketing Team

Note from BioHapHazard - I just wanted to point out that the marketing team currently consists of members from the community that have stepped up to offer help with marketing and social media. They are all people with real life marketing and social media managing experience and expertise. If you are interested in being included in this team and have relevant experience, please get in touch with me.
